anything about good outcomes.

196
00:13:19.335 --> 00:13:22.035
It ignores the possibility
of good outcomes.

197
00:13:22.035 --> 00:13:26.745
At the other end of the spectrum,
there are maxi-max strategies.

198
00:13:26.745 --> 00:13:30.015
Those are actions that
maximize the maximum outcome.

199
00:13:31.255 --> 00:13:35.435
They seek good outcomes, but then again
they completely ignore bad outcomes.

